data.description: Located in Laurel Vista with community pool in walking distance. Corner lot. Brick and siding home. Vinyl wood flooring welcome you as you walk into entry area. Main bedroom with ensuite bathroom is located downstairs. Additional bedrooms and loft(second living area) are carpeted upstairs. Has separate dining area with modern chandelier and laundry room located downstairs. Patio area in backyard with privacy wood fencing.
